cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CV, cs.DM, cs.NE 

The paper deals with machine learning algorithms, specifically Support Vector Machines (SVMs), and proposes a new method for boosting SVMs to improve their performance on class imbalance and small disjuncts. This falls under the category of "Machine Learning" (cs.LG) and "Artificial Intelligence" (cs.AI). The paper also discusses the use of SVMs in computer vision (cs.CV) and data mining (cs.DM) applications. Additionally, the proposed method involves modifying the SVM kernel, which is a common technique in neural networks (cs.NE).
